title: 10 Most Hated Country Songs + Amy's Plumber Takes Control of Music + Chicken Nugget Eating Competition
itunes:title: 10 Most Hated Country Songs + Amy's Plumber Takes Control of Music + Chicken Nugget Eating Competition
description:
A list of the most hated country songs of all-time and Bobby reads them off to see if the studio loves it, hates it or is indifferent about it. Plus, Amy's plumber shows her a new music genre when doing work at her house. After a girl sets a new world record for most chicken nuggets eaten in one minute, the studio is inspired to hold a nugget competition of their own.
